{"tid":25410,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[胃酸倒流] 食梗長期減胃酸藥既入一入黎 可能有用","createTime":"2016-12-06T06:05:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T13:54:35.000Z","uid":9541,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a3b1a2d9c013c88bee9cdbb7b520239aa5682797","tid":25410,"uid":9541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:05:27.000Z","msg":"利申先 我四年前倒開始有胃病<br />\n長期胃酸多 倒流<br />\n一食完野就頂住喉嚨 嘔翻曬出黎<br />\n咁果時係美國睇醫生就開左隻ppi 胃藥<br />\n初期食好有用 一日一粒 之後食乜都無問題<br />\n如是者 一食就食左三年幾<br />\n直到有一日 兩個月前倒 發覺無乜效<br />\n食完一樣反胃加嘔<br />\n之前照過胃西醫都係話無特別原因 <br />\n係壓力或食野習慣做成<br />\n結果都係開ppi俾我<br />\n<br />\n直到有一日我女朋友上網幫我揾到一個方法<br />\n係蘋果醋沖水每日早上飲一杯<br />\n我就停左藥之後開始飲 一個星期後啲徵狀真係無乜咁濟<br />\n<br />\n原理係話 胃係有detect 你胃內既酸度<br />\n如果酸度不足就會generate 胃酸去補<br />\n而大部分胃酸多既病人多數係因為胃既酸度唔夠強<br />\n蘋果醋溝水原因就係補翻個酸度從而令胃停止generate acid. <br />\n而ppi就係強制stop 個胃去generate 但最後因為慣性左而無用<br />\n令到胃酸度唔夠佢又generate 翻<br />\n<br />\n你地如果同我有同一問題同一個病<br />\n我完全明白有幾辛苦<br />\n可以一試<br />\n<br />\nBtw 好多謝我女朋友迫我用呢個方法<br />\n原本我係應酬心態去試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9494190572c298cf283cef623cd9fd940a53c18","tid":25410,"uid":3146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:11:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dd59a18224beaf239899046d4f3ebe1cf900120","tid":25410,"uid":9541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:11:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"089f4f71bf801e43ba17dddc2346b3beda59e4e5","tid":25410,"uid":9541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:12:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc6f3fe1dea2a071312f1b9e541efa157876e1d","tid":25410,"uid":11082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:13:17.000Z","msg":"加維斯康好似ok既"},{"pid":"2ef15b92a1d6e2bcdc28c61e37ced0a1a04c0603","tid":25410,"uid":9541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:14:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加維斯康好似ok既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個無研究過<br />\n但親身飲梗蘋果醋溝水"},{"pid":"8bdca57fd038dc469fba542c7cc2e9367e62136e","tid":25410,"uid":9541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:24:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01426c38ea9688d0db19e378e86ceab321c8749e","tid":25410,"uid":9541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:14:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"728640fc21439b4af409e0d1a811335d94ebdc4f","tid":25410,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01426c38ea9688d0db19e378e86ceab321c8749e","tid":25410,"uid":9541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:14:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T13:54:35.000Z","msg":"你有好女友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}